Package structure5

Class CharSet

java.lang.Object
structure5.CharSet
public class CharSet extends Object
Implementation of a set of characters whose ASCII values are between 0 and 255, inclusive. This set is specialized for use with characters. It is implemented using the BitSet class. This class's interface differs from the Set,
invalid @link 
java.util.Bitset
, and Set interfaces, so care must be taken to invoke the proper methods.
Author:
, 2001 duane a. bailey
